{"tid":738361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國左膠新聞網VOX係支那資助 請勿中伏","createTime":"2018-07-11T12:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T07:57:27.000Z","uid":4493,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5f75427866ece9b9bfa1a8873a9592e89eea65","tid":738361,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"見有巴打見佢準備報道香港好興奮<br />\n要提提大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【國際聯繫】Vox下週三開始播片介紹香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/738271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/738271</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n【董建華有份】美媒Vox被指收北京錢 寫「中國成大贏家」新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180615/58320123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320123&d=0RoAtFcd%2FKvjBHT0hgqWWL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=11e07c6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320123&h=7ee1f913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180615/58320123</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 美國著名新聞網站Vox，被發現收取中國政府支持的組織資金，撰寫軟性新聞文章。<br />\n<br />\n最近Vox外電編輯Yochi Dreazen一篇新聞，標題為「特金會最大贏家？中國」（The big winner of the Trump-Kim summit? China）。在文章底部，特別註明了它是由中美交流基金會資助。<br />\n<br />\n文章最底的註解寫道：「這篇報道是由中美交流基金會（CUSEF）資助，它是一間總部在香港的私人資助非牟利機構，致力『促使中美兩國的政策制定者、商界領袖、學者、智庫、文化界及教育工作者，進行開放且有建設性的交流』。」這個介紹跟中美交流基金會網站的英文介紹用字同出一轍。<br />\n<br />\n中美交流基金會是中國政府支持的組織，在海外宣傳中國，「廣告新聞」首先由《華爾街日報》專欄作家Josh Rogin發現。Rogin在Twitter質問Vox：「你知道CUSEF由中國共產黨內具影響力的一名高級官員當主席，對吧？（他就是）董建華，CUSEF的主席是中國全國政協副主席，（全國政協）與在海外推動黨目標的統戰部有關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前，美國國會議員致力反擊中國利用美國傳媒作政治宣傳，Vox跟中美交流基金會的關係更受關注。參議院2018年度國防授權法案中，特別提到「中國正透過影響美國傳媒、文化機構、商家、學術及政策社群，對其安全、軍事政策和目標更加有利」。近月，中美交流基金會也因為被指滲透德州大學奧斯汀分校，被美國國會盯上。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/205003_e25cf687995498e59a4461b0f920a0fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F205003_e25cf687995498e59a4461b0f920a0fb.png&h=062a82ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c6f6b99689bef1037dbb97cd4b3f132113ba914","tid":738361,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9b5172b8008f47529561b21c7b5fcac461b436","tid":738361,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想扮fox<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23a4ce8bc2a77d9bf2edb24a2c1c834e86efc8c","tid":738361,"uid":3241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"中美交流基金會係借香港向海外輸出共產"},{"pid":"aa6a48a88514c657bccaad95edc6fb71c5af159c","tid":738361,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9b5172b8008f47529561b21c7b5fcac461b436","tid":738361,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想扮fox<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"本身撈得幾掂<br />\n<br />\n侵上台後收收地皮 要RMB打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465fe46cb83c01d621d3b11082f55d2302b57183","tid":738361,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d23a4ce8bc2a77d9bf2edb24a2c1c834e86efc8c","tid":738361,"uid":3241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"中美交流基金會係借香港向海外輸出共產"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"習思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr